Interface HashShortShortMap

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface HashShortShortMap
extends ShortShortMap, HashContainer
    An interface for ShortShortMaps, based on hash tables.

    This interface doesn't carry own specific behaviour, just combines it's superinterfaces.

    Looking for a way to instantiate a HashShortShortMap? See static factory methods in HashShortShortMaps class.
